twitch_info.title: I Wanna Be The Ocean Princess Part 6
twitch_info.description: We slog through the beach, and get to an interesting level. Much like the Temple of Trials from stage 4, it has several unique gimmicks wrapped up into one stage, in addition to some cool underwater sub gameplay (or you could platform, but nahhh).
